            "id": 78645,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Jusqu'à présent, nous avons appris à créer une boucle <code>while</code>, concentrons-nous maintenant sur la façon de les empêcher de boucler indéfiniment.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Creating the variable",
            "id": 78648,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Pour arrêter une boucle, nous commençons par créer une variable en dehors de la boucle.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"10\" /><option startIndex=\"11\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\":\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>keep_going</code> suivi de <code>=</code> et enfin <code>True</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variable in the condition",
            "id": 78647,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nous utilisons la variable dans la condition pour décider si la boucle doit exécuter son bloc de code ou non. Par exemple, <code>keep_going == True</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"43\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>keep_going</code> suivi de <code>==</code> et enfin <code>True</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Updating the variable",
            "id": 78670,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>À l'intérieur du bloc de code, nous arrêtons la boucle en définissant <code>keep_going</code> sur <code>False</code> afin que la condition renvoie <code>False</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_going = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"81\" endIndex=\"86\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de rentrer <code>False</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Stopping the loop",
            "id": 78644,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>La boucle exécute l'intégralité de son bloc de code parce que <code>keep_going</code> est <code>True</code> au début, mais ne s'exécute pas à nouveau si nous définissons <code>keep_going</code> à <code>False</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"keep_going = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keep_going == \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  keep_going = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;one more time&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"one more time\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
